Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.64,0:01:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪惡存在天理不容！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.60,0:01:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Funny Storm！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.67,0:01:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說這傢伙啊  到底在和什麼戰鬥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.01,0:01:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪惡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.92,0:01:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…那再具體一點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.19,0:01:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪惡魔法組合
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.10,0:01:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.46,0:01:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把這個世界陷入一片混亂與恐懼之中的集合啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.91,0:01:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組合嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.55,0:02:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果敗給這些傢伙的話會怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.07,0:02:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  這是她必須做的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.41,0:02:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,複雜的設定吾不曉得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.58,0:02:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？那這好看嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.14,0:02:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連為什麼在戰鬥都不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.12,0:02:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有辦法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.33,0:02:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾也是來這裡之後才開始看的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的十三話  秋葉說要給我看的可還…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.48,0:02:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  都怪仁說一些沒用的害得吾錯過精彩片段了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.03,0:02:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.56,0:02:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Handsom Storm！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.45,0:02:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grow Up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎…這樣嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Magical那個啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒！ 就是這樣——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:02:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  從電視裡學到的還真是多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對更加強大的敵人力量升級也是必須的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  吾的「大麻」差不多也該升下級啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是兩碼事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.91,0:03:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是還能用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能用也已經是很危險的狀態了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前  最近的你不也只是在玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又去K歌  又看新番的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.42,0:03:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾…吾打算明天起再開始做的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著我的眼睛說啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說虧心話不怕鬼哭床嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  像這種商品隨便找個店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.77,0:03:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要讓看到的人不呆掉就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個修好繼續用吧  好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Handsom Storm
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grow Up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊——我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從雞塊便當裡把雞肉吃光的話不只剩下白飯了嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,@#%$&%^(^*%$%#$
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼我聽不懂啊！還給我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.02,0:04:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的重大發表請注意～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實呢  我懺悔妹妹目前正在錄製CD～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  也就是說懺悔妹妹歌手出道決定對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  還沒有決定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.99,0:04:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  現在募集想讓我出道的唱片公司～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.93,0:04:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯絡地址就這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…懺悔妹妹  請不要擅自佔用我們的節目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.09,0:04:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌詞已經寫好啦  請多關照～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉OK讓她嘗到甜頭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  身為神也太容易隨波逐流了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你  沒資格說人家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.77,0:04:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  你這樣的男人居然會和懺悔妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才更能給予她幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.88,0:04:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此…礙事者一律…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐嚇電話啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近很多的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:04:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懺悔妹妹相關的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:05:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受歡迎的男人真不好過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊  還不是因為你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能配得上我家的大鐵君啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠理解大鐵君心情的只有我啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  吾先去洗個澡算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天起又要開始繁忙的汙穢退治了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你分明是故意的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那以後過了挺長時間了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.89,0:06:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出來了哦  仁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.03,0:06:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥  三千元左右的話去買也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天放學後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.09,0:06:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從明天起繼續用這個哼哼哈兮除汙穢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.38,0:06:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要拜託仁哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.56,0:06:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汙穢存在天理不容！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.69,0:06:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:06:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:06:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.47,0:07:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.59,0:07:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.57,0:07:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是災難啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.86,0:07:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  就是他哦  四角關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.78,0:07:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個來者不拒的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.41,0:07:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fsp120}　{\fsp1}camouflage{\r}\N也有說那是在掩飾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.43,0:07:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然不是很冷清的男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來為什麼他一臉傷？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然修羅場就是這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了好幾次了  最好和薙小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…看來暫時不靠近你為好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你必須警惕那個女人  明白？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.59,0:07:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是來者不拒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御廚迎來了他的最受歡迎時期
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最受歡迎時期？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.91,0:08:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂最受歡迎時期
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是任何人都會遇到的莫名其妙大受歡迎的時期
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.49,0:08:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不局限於容貌人格  一生之內必將來臨一次的時期
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但可怕的是這個時期的反動力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.05,0:08:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年輕的時候過度受歡迎的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長大之後就再也沒有那種人緣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.08,0:08:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換句話說就是女禍之相
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.91,0:08:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實有能聯想到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如今天的這傷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.55,0:08:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不注意從窗戶摔出去怎麼可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.28,0:08:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來你的傷還真多啊  御廚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是貼著OK繃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.84,0:08:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太不懂得保護身體了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明告誡過要注意身體的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.31,0:08:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你  讓啥物體上身了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別說那麼不吉利的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附身之物嘛  那東西  就讓吾來祓除吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,kira☆kira☆kira☆kira☆kira☆kira☆kira☆kira☆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女禍…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:02.53,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（dj：仁你真靈光=_,=||）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.74,0:09:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最受歡迎時期啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中男生的話應該是歡呼雀躍的狀況吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.47,0:09:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道御廚是塊死木頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家裡和薙小姐同居！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.23,0:09:16.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薙：「先吃飯？還是先洗澡？或者是說……」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學校又被鶇和懺悔妹妹巧語所迷！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:18.98,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶇：「下次我們一起去看電影吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:20.76,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懺悔：「哎～～～也帶上我嘛～～～」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是何等的紅旗不倒彩旗飄飄的日在校園啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.90,0:09:22.61,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶇：「怎麼辦啊？」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.88,0:09:23.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懺悔：「好想去仁家裡啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.92,0:09:25.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薙：「一起去吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:25.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs17}（dj：誠哥的時代結束啦XD）\N（WindEndless：現在是中古神+人渣仁嗎）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.19,0:09:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的話哈喇子都流滿地了啊  這狀況！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來沒辦法了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.11,0:09:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼被自己不喜歡的女孩子表示愛意也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在有真正喜歡的人的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼啊  把我拖到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我已經到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先被人懷疑同性戀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後又被叫做是無差別
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.97,0:09:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又被搞得滿身繃帶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底不都是你弄的嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯  這個吾承認
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女禍…我好像真中了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:09:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  最近又被鶇看到了我的寶貝…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.02,0:10:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶貝？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去我會被殺！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要求改善我的待遇！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來我都是恍恍惚惚地跟著你團團轉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可不行了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  突然間…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你是神所以相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可再這樣下去我身子骨都會撐不住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從此和我商量好之後再給我行動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到今天沒有懷疑你的我也有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也在各種各樣的曖昧之下熬到了今天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來你到底為什麼住在我家裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡要解釋清楚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.62,0:10:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…和吾之前說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.06,0:10:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾是為了清除汙穢而現身此地的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集信仰也是為此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個汙穢我也不是很明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.57,0:10:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個嗎？哪裡都會有的東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少會以蜘蛛和千足蟲的形態出現
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以昆蟲的形式出現絕非一般
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然蟲子這麼多很不正常吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.19,0:11:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我們鎮？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.13,0:11:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.78,0:11:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天曉得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.39,0:11:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…天曉得算啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候起出現的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天曉得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.05,0:11:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候出來的也不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.61,0:11:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看來你好像是隱瞞著什麼的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.72,0:11:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你告訴我這個好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會以昆蟲的形態出現呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.93,0:11:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是蛾子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  汙穢出來的話  會糟糕成什麼樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.42,0:11:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被附身的話就會發生不好的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾一碰到就會被玷汙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.88,0:11:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你因為那莫名其妙的汙穢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會釀出什麼壞事而滿街退治它們吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.49,0:12:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和昨天的動畫片沒區別嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.00,0:12:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難道沒想過自己為什麼要這麼做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝做什麼！ 不是說不要再追問了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.57,0:12:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全忘了嗎？ 笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.46,0:12:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又發脾氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一談起這事請就會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.61,0:12:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前總是這樣岔開話題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可沒那麼容易了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.58,0:12:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃苦頭的人可是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不知道就給我想清楚！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薙小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.31,0:12:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是來者不拒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.84,0:12:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天曉得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:12:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那反應是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.97,0:13:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往棉花堆打拳白費力氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恍恍惚惚的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切好似燈火闌珊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切曖昧糾纏不清…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你最好再稍微努力一些會更好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.18,0:13:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是聽到你和我女兒有三角戀情的關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心就感情用事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝茶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.30,0:13:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了…既然誤會已經解開了的話那我就先…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受夠了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.44,0:13:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.65,0:13:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得有點怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.85,0:13:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家女兒竟然會喜歡上你這樣的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有些事情想和你談
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上是關於薙的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  薙同學啊  有什麼可以找我談的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她其實是個神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是這麼說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.97,0:14:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁這個大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾煩個什麼吶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  原來她…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我是頭一次聽說這種事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.71,0:14:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是神嗎  薙同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神明啊…神明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這麼一個人的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.27,0:14:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說感性太高了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.16,0:14:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些人有時對於某種反應會產生人格上的變化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.31,0:14:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人說這是精神上的疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有人說靈學說上的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:14:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有被人說做是惡魔附身或者靈媒體質一類的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這種奇異的人格有時也會是虛假的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是冠以神明惡魔之名而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薙她是…妖怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅憑這些還無法斷定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.21,0:15:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但越是低俗之靈便越是想冒充高尚的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然也不是說她一定就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.14,0:15:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是舉個例子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.52,0:15:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可要真是這樣…我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要除去體內的靈體就要進行洗禮  或者除魔等是手段
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我覺得她們…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我覺得她們並不是那麼壞的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薙同學是從神社的神木雕像中顯現的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:16:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本的神道和其他國家的宗教比起來思想顯得十分多樣化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以說是百家爭鳴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對的信仰和偶像崇拜也不在少數
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.92,0:16:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先從八百萬神明這點來看  神是不看類別的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.08,0:16:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以對她們來說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.56,0:16:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確定一個實體才是第一步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實體…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.35,0:16:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我認為不是壞東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  沒有什麼可以稱做是神的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是薙自己說她是神…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.53,0:16:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是這麼說了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.53,0:16:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼線索嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者說是能證明她是神的證據？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.11,0:16:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法辯解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.65,0:16:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的庸俗作風又是最好的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.14,0:16:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的言行和舉止十分含糊不明  讓人揣測無方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.83,0:16:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但正因為此  她有可能是陷入這樣的性格之中無法自拔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.15,0:17:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的話會這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們是為了自己的某種目的而在冒充神明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是堅信自己就是神明的兩者之一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此田此土  乃吾之身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.93,0:17:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾孕之子  皆吾愛子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬般可憐  吾之所愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.92,0:18:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可喜可賀  甚之幸哉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.57,0:18:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只願諸君  茁壯成長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此一盼  吾意足矣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.24,0:18:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸甚樂甚  為神福甚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了這片土地  吾一定要消滅這些汙穢之物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些很難對付
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.98,0:18:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我們鎮？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.59,0:18:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己也不明白？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.15,0:18:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.48,0:18:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後仁就說「我要尋找自我！」就參加了美術社
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我覺得只是模仿大鐵君也沒什麼意義啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.71,0:18:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15歲的孩子怎麼能看清那個地步嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  連我自己都不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.79,0:18:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果能找到自我是最好的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼樣找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.87,0:19:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種問題  就算想也沒用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白的時候  靠感情和直覺行動就是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾一直都是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去想那些不明白的事情也毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠感情和直覺行動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠感情和直覺行動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為你的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我添了大亂子了  你明不明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…這沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算去考慮也沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不和我說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧我還這樣照顧你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴！ 不要問了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道的事情不去想就行了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡  這樣生活  有什麼不好！有什麼不當嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝在懷疑身為神靈的吾所說的話嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:19:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前總是這樣岔開話題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:19:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可沒那麼容易了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.69,0:20:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不知道就給我想清楚！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.02,0:20:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.43,0:20:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來吾自己也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.48,0:20:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然連自己為什麼不知道…也不明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.93,0:20:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何  不知道她的話就應該知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是自稱卻沒有實據的神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.18,0:20:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真能和這種不明來頭的傢伙同居這麼長時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.33,0:21:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半斤八兩嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.14,0:21:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？ 只有這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.74,0:21:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御祭神不明？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.39,0:21:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正體不明也要有個限度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.57,0:21:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的事情要怎麼調查才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.59,0:21:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有正式記錄的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能直接去找相關人員了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薙？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.12,0:23:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回的神薙…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.24,0:23:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁  你怎麼了？
